    "content": "## Tools\n*   **Aider**: GPT-5 models supported; Grok-4 supported; Gemini 2.5 Flash Lite supported; `/clear` prints message; `/undo` output shows first line; MoonshotAI Kimi-K2 supported.\n*   **Claude Code**: StopFailure hook event; `${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_DATA}` variable; frontmatter supports effort, maxTurns; Terminal notifications reach outer terminal; Max output token limits increased; `allowRead` sandbox setting; `/copy` accepts index; MCP elicitation support; New Elicitation, ElicitationResult hooks; `-n`/`--name` CLI flag; `worktree.sparsePaths` setting; `/context` actionable suggestions; `autoMemoryDirectory` setting; `modelOverrides` setting; OAuth actionable guidance; Tool search bypasses proxy gate; `w` key in `/copy` writes to file; `/plan` optional description; `claude plugins` alias; ExitWorktree tool; `/loop` command; Cron scheduling tools; `voice:pushToTalk` keybinding; Bash auto-approval allowlist expanded; `/claude-api` skill added; `Ctrl+U` exits bash mode; Numeric keypad support; `/remote-control` optional name.\n*   **Ollama**: Web Search, Fetch in OpenClaw; `ollama signin` command; `ollama launch openclaw` command; Improved OpenClaw Kimi-K2.5 performance; Tool calling accuracy improved; Ollama is OpenClaw provider.\n*   **Codex CLI**: Full-resolution image inspection; `js_repl` exposes `codex.cwd`, `codex.homeDir`; Realtime websocket transcription mode; `codex` tool v2 handoff.\n\n## SDKs\n*   **OpenAI SDK**: 5.4 nano, mini model slugs; `/v1/videos` batches endpoint; `ToolFunction` `defer_loading` field; `ComparisonFilter` `in`, `nin` operators; Custom voices; Sora API improvements (character API, video extensions); `ComputerTool` class used; GPT-5.4, tool search tool, new computer tool; `phase` added; `gpt-realtime-1.5`, `gpt-audio-1.5` models; Websockets for responses API; Container `network_policy` and skills; Images in batch API.\n*   **Anthropic SDK**: GA `thinking-display-setting`; `array_format` to brackets; MCP tools conversion helpers; Top-level cache control; New tool versions as types; Claude Sonnet 4.6 released; Fast-mode for Claude Opus 4.6; Claude Opus 4.6 released; Structured Outputs support; `output_config` for structured outputs; Custom JSON encoder added.\n\n## CLI\n*   **Gemini CLI**: Customizable keyboard shortcuts; Thread AgentLoopContext; Vim mode motions added; Retry fetch notifications; Chat resume footer on session quit; Bold, styles in SVG snapshots; Semantic focus colors; History visibility enhanced.\n\n## BREAKING\n*   **OpenAI SDK**: `prompt_cache_key` removed from responses; `phase` field removed from message types."
  }
]